<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000031/2025-26> a ns1:CourseGuide ;
    ns1:hasCompetency <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000031/2025-26/CE02>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000031/2025-26/CE03>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000031/2025-26/CE05>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000031/2025-26/CE10>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000031/2025-26/CG03>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000031/2025-26/CG05>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000031/2025-26/CT07> ;
    ns1:hasDidacticResource <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000031/2025-26/didactic_resource/1>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000031/2025-26/didactic_resource/2>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000031/2025-26/didactic_resource/3>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000031/2025-26/didactic_resource/4> ;
    ns1:hasEvaluation <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000031/2025-26/evaluation> ;
    ns1:hasLearningResult <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000031/2025-26/RA36>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000031/2025-26/RA37>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000031/2025-26/RA38> ;
    ns1:hasSyllabus <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000031/2025-26/syllabus> ;
    ns1:inpersonHours "28 horas (35.9%)"@es ;
    ns1:numberOfCredits 3.0 ;
    ns1:otherInformation "We will emphasize the practical use of the tools and techniques explained in the course. The Use of Generative AI will strictly forbidden (and penalized) for all assignments"@es ;
    ns1:periodEndingMonth "Enero"@es ;
    ns1:periodStartingMonth "Septiembre"@es ;
    ns1:teachingPeriod "2025-26" ;
    ns1:teachingPeriodMonths "Septiembre-Enero"@es ;
    ns1:totalHours "28 horas"@es ;
    schema:activitiesWorkload "100%"@es ;
    schema:courseSchedule <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000031/2025-26/eventSchedule> ;
    schema:description """Biomedical informatics is a scientific discipline created in the 1960s with the intention of improving the management of data, information and knowledge in the biomedical area. Achievements include the creation of decision support systems, electronic medical records, omic projects, hospital information systems, terminologies and other projects of similar importance. The creation of the so-called digital medicine and precision medicine are the latest advances in this direction, seeking ubiquitous computing, with the goal of improving the health of the citizen. Artificial Intelligence is a key topic in this regard.
There will be a survey of bioinfomatics techniques, from a practical perspective, and of Artificial Intelligence, including recent developments related to Large Language Models and their applications in medicine.
The management of data and knowledge in health has its own characteristics. The design of the studies and the evaluation of the results, for example, are completely different from those that are necessary in other multiple areas."""@es ;
    schema:director <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/victormanuel.maojo%40upm.es> ;
    schema:inLanguage "Inglés"@es ;
    schema:instructor <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/jose.crespo%40upm.es>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/miguel.garcia.remesal%40upm.es>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/victormanuel.maojo%40upm.es> ;
    schema:name "Manejo de Datos y Conocimiento en la Salud"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000031/2025-26/CE02> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CE02" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Utilizar sistemas operativos, programas y herramientas de uso común en biología computacional, así como, manejar plataformas de cómputo de altas prestaciones, lenguajes de programación y análisis bioinformáticos/ Utilizing operative systems, software and tools commonly used in computational biology, and working with high throughput platforms, programing languages and bioinformatics tools."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000031/2025-26/CE03> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CE03" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Analizar e interpretar bioinformáticamente los datos que se derivan de las tecnologías ómicas, y proponer soluciones bioinformáticas en relación a dichos datos/ Analyzing and interpreting bioinformatically data derived from ?omics technologies, and proposing bioinformatics solutions according to such data."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000031/2025-26/CE05> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CE05" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Utilizar herramientas de biología computacional para el análisis genómico, incluida la genómica comparativa y biología evolutiva/ Using computational biology tools for genomics analyses, including comparative genomics and evolutionary biology."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000031/2025-26/CE10> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CE10" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Conocimiento de las técnicas de representación del conocimiento reutilizables y modelos de razonamiento en entornos centralizados y distribuidos a utilizar en la resolución de problemas que impliquen conducta inteligente/ Knowing reusable techniques for knowledge representation and reasoning models in centralized and distributed environments, and when to used them for problem solving."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000031/2025-26/CG03> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CG03" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Que los estudiantes sepan aplicar los conocimientos adquiridos y su capacidad de resolución de problemas en entornos nuevos o poco conocidos dentro de contextos más amplios (o multidisciplinares) relacionados con el area de la Biología Computacional/ Provide students with the ability to apply the acquired knowledge to solve problems in new environments within ample or multidisciplinary contexts in the field of Computational Biology."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000031/2025-26/CG05> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CG05" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Que los estudiantes sean capaces de integrar conocimientos en el area de la Biología Computacional, de formular conclusiones, hipótesis o líneas de trabajo a partir de la información disponible, y de formarse una opinion fundamentada sobre las responsabilidades sociales y éticas vinculadas a la aplicación de sus conocimientos/ Provide students with the capacity to integrate knowledge in the area of Computational Biology, formulate conclusions, hypotheses or research lines from the available information, and with the ability to elaborate solid opinions about the social and ethic responsibilities derived from the application of their knowledge."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000031/2025-26/CT07> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CT07" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Ser capaz de manejar las tecnologías de la información y comunicación en un contexto profesional/ Be able of working with information and media technologies in a professional context."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000031/2025-26/RA36> a ns1:LearningResult ;
    ns1:learningResultCode "RA36" ;
    ns1:learningResultDescription "Adquirir los conocimientos para la gestión de datos del área de salud"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/203000031/2025-26/RA37> a ns1:LearningResult ;
